Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:00.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:05.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}悄悄地让过去
